Useful tools for authoring preview screenshots
==============================================



Mac OSX Tools:


GIMP
----
Great for cropping, adding transparency, compression

LICEcap
-------
Great for recording animated gifs

Digital Color Meter
-------------------
Useful for grabbing on screen colors



Web tools:


https://onlinegiftools.com/create-transparent-gif
-------------------------------------------------
Useful for keying out a single color from a gif to add transparency

